item.title: Avoiding the Bear Trap - Live from Future Proof
item.description: The Express steams through the Future Proof Wealth Festival to bring you conversations from some of the country's top financial advisors and investment strategists on how we should navigate the tumult in the capital markets. Joe McLean, Lindsey Bell, Blair Duquesnay and Michael Antonelli climb aboard with their best advice for investors of all ages as we face rising interest rates and even more uncertainty... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/investopediaexpress
